Example raw cause-of-death dataset

Source: R/data.R
cod_data_raw_example.Rd

Example raw cause-of-death dataset

Usage

cod_data_raw_example

Format

A data frame with 6 columns and 20 rows:

VariableDescription
idUnique identifier
sexSex of deceased
ageAge of diseased in years
codeICD 11 cause-of-death code
dodDate of death
dobDate of birth

Examples

cod_data_raw_example
